						</div>
			</div>
</div>
</div><a name="eztoc417501_4" id="eztoc417501_4"></a><h2>The Perfect Fit for Digital Experiences</h2><p><a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/New-eZ-Publish-Platform-5.3-Easier-to-Build-a-Solid-Content-Business" target="_self">The eZ Publish Platform</a> is positioned as a true enterprise CMS platform. Being Open Sourced, it is an ideal platform to enable a truly customized and integrated enterprise wide platform for digital marketing. eZ is celebrating 15 years in the industry with a long track record of being an enterprise ready CMS, with many business relying on the platform for content in industries such as media groups, banks, telecomm , brand conglomerates, public and nonprofit institutions. &nbsp;</p><p>The eZ Publish Platform is truly a platform to help break down silos and enable a true omni-channel marketing approach, something not possible with closed systems. When it comes to focusing on KPI driven conversions and integration with your business applications, we truly believe we have become a leader in the field.</p>
    </div>

